info.name: Feabie Dark Theme
info.description: Light-on dark low-to-moderate-contrast colour scheme for Feabie.
info.additionalInfo:
Does not attempt to re-colour the notifications pop-down thing.
Probably contains some other errors and/or omissions.

Use at your own risk! I mean, it just changes the colours of stuff, but it could still inadvertently make something invisible or non-obvious that was supposed to be obvious and visible and Feabie could change stuff in the future which breaks it.

Changes:
2020-10-26 Fix image masks because Feabie appended ?v=3 to some image urls.
2020-07-10 Fix image masks because Feabie appended ?v=2 to some image urls.
2018-05-17 Styled new messages to match dark theme in message list.
2018-04-28 Masked and re-coloured search box AJAX loading bar to match dark surroundings.
2018-03-07 Extended dark theme to cover weight charts on profiles.
2018-03-05 Masked the large drawings of people so they don't appear with a white background.
2018-03-04 Initial release.
